<p>Cement dust forms a fine powder that settles across flooring after renovation work.</p>
<h2>Why cement dust spreads</h2>
<p>Fine particles travel easily through the property during construction activity.</p>
<h2>Cleaning method</h2>
<p>HEPA vacuuming followed by damp microfibre cleaning removes cement residue effectively.</p>
